title: Weather Cancels Final Day of South Carolina Fall Classic for @OspreyWTEN
text: | North Florida Athletics Weather Cancels Final Day of South Carolina Fall Classic for @OspreyWTEN COLUMBIA, S.C. â€“ Due to overnight heavy rain and flooding, the final day of the South Carolina Fall Classic was cancelled. University of North Florida women's tennis finished the weekend with eight victories. UNF returns to action in two weekends with the Bedford Cup Oct. 16-18 that is being held at the FGCU Tennis Complex.
